<title>MALAYSIA: Gold Bridge soars after bonus news.</title>
<headline>Gold Bridge soars after bonus news.</headline>
<dateline>KUALA LUMPUR 1997-07-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares of requoted Malaysian construction firm Gold Bridge Engineering &amp; Construction Bhd soared in early Thursday trading after announcing a one-for-one bonus issue plan.</p>
<p>Around 10 minutes into trading, the stock was up 1.40 ringgit or 11.97 percent to 13.10 on volume of 39,000 shares traded.</p>
<p>The company on Wednesday announced a plan to issue a one-for-one bonus and said it also planned to jointly build a shopping mall.</p>
<p>-- Kuala Lumpur newsroom (603-201 4813)</p>
